com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport

Class ProhibitedOperation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.model.schema.transport.ProhibitedOperation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProhibitedCreate, ProhibitedEdit, ProhibitedRetrieve

    public abstract class ProhibitedOperation
extends Object
    An indicator that a user operation is prohibited for items, property groups, or properties of a particular type, as defined in a Schema.

    Prohibitions on user operations are enforced by i2 Analyze services. Standard and custom services are responsible for ensuring that clients cannot perform prohibited operations.

    Since:
    5.0
